Bazooka!  Ayo!

00:13:24.720 --> 00:13:27.000
Apa yang kamu katakan...
- Hei, Shalu!

00:13:27.080 --> 00:13:29.120
Kami mendapat izin.
Ayo, kita bertemu Lakshmi.

00:13:29.200 --> 00:13:31.320
Kami mendapat izin!  - Ya ya ya!

